>  has been re-indexed to lower the truck. Nothing has been cut or welded
>  (thankfully  !!) What is the appropriate angle and the best way to re-set 
the
>  rear torsion bar/arm. The rear arm is under no tension whith the rear in 
the
>  air and the transaxle removed.
>  
